--cut "My background in Digital Advertising, Data-Driven Strategies, and Integrated Marketing has allowed me to excel in driving results for various campaigns."
--Change "Securing the Working Families Party's ballot line in New York with a mobilization campaign that significantly outperformed the Democratic Party turnout. This effort played a major role in holding key Congressional districts, supporting endorsed candidates in high-profile primary, general, and runoff elections, and set an online fundraising record for a single campaign with over $55k raised in two months." to "Securing the Working Families Party's ballot line in New York with a mobilization campaign that significantly outperformed the Democratic Party turnout and played a major role in holding key Congressional districts, in addition to breaking the online fundraising record for a single campaign with over $55k raised in two months."
--This is a bit cliche: As the digital landscape continues to evolve, I remain committed to staying ahead of industry trends and utilizing my skills to help clients achieve their goals.
